CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 8, 1945, pg. 2, reads: "School Days - Lovely sub-deb Leta Moore is one of the many students who are pursuing their scholastics with enthusiasm at the Herron Hill Junior High School.  She is the granddaughter of the Rev. T. J. King. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Leta Moore holding books and standing on stairs, with young man leaning on rail in background, Herron Hill Junior High School
